Firestrike saw the blast and was able to duck in time, unfortuanatly 
bringing his face into the sweeping motion of Prowls leg snapping 
his head around and spinning the immense bot.  Scrambling to his 
feet he pointed his sword straight at Prowl.  "One or Two" he 
asked.  Suddenly the sword opened like a giant mouth fireing two 
rockets over the three foot range at Prowl.  The rockets would have 
a small explsion but would ignite any target on impact with a 
degree of fire to melt almost anything slowly.
